text: Ararat Chronicle and Willaura and Lake Bolac Districts Recorder was a newspaper published in Ararat, Victoria, Australia. == History == The newspaper was first published on 23 January 1909 and ceased publication . == Digitisation == Issues from 1914 to 1918 have been digitised and are available on Trove. == References == == External links == * Category:Defunct newspapers published in Victoria (Australia) Category:Ararat, Victoria
